            <article>
                <section>
                    <h2>Introduction</h2>
                    <div class="blog-flex"> <p>Nodemon is a popular utility that
                            helps develop Node.js applications by automatically
                            restarting the node application when file changes in
                            the directory are detected. However, sometimes
                            developers encounter issues where Nodemon doesn't
                            run properly. This blog provides a detailed guide on
                            how to troubleshoot and resolve common Nodemon
                            issues in NPM.</p>
                        <img src="img/nodemon-logo.png"
